              Each element of
              <b>
               piles
              </b>
              will be between 0 and 1000 inclusive.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              At least one element of
              <b>
               piles
              </b>
              other than the last element will be larger than 0.
             </td>
